 formulas.\n\nHis stern, sure-fire and entirely present persona, cuts him an interesting character in the world of games. One thing is for sure; we haven’t seen the last of the man known for his sock-less feet, a slight Eastern Holland accent, with a Partagas-Havana No 2 cigar in the corner of his mouth and an iPhone stuck to his ear.\nSpecialties\n\nMarketing, Finance, Legal, Acquisition, Mergers/joint ventures & Business Development\n','2011-06-29 10:07:28','2011-07-05 01:10:08',NULL,0,1,NULL,'717807174',6469092,13,'lots of fun and games :)','F7ow-g4fBP','reinouttebrake',NULL,'6469092-auvgz0SwnVAmzkK5BCVxtPM23zMCyh6GuyJpVe78','hm2exdeFK54RupUtBe1XXCcNj6yozjXl2o5HzZOP4Q',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0),(490,'inge.vanderkraan@kenniskring.nl','','minipush32','Inge','van der Kraan',0,'','Assistent at KennisKring Amsterdam (Amsterdam Knowledge Network Foundation)','2011-06-29 10:19:23','2011-06-29 10:19:23','2011/06/29/03_19_23_134_file',0,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,2,'...','dDgKy9H8cG',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'3506b7ca-22bc-4dc0-855d-1cb0b38b7d82','c06750eb-c0d5-42f9-9a68-9f66875f6abe','http://www.linkedin.com/in/ingevanderkraan',0,0),(491,'eddy@beeblebrox.nl','','xrayblue17','Eddy','Boeve',0,'','Resultant bij de freelancefirm. Voor al uw online professionals','2011-06-29 10:23:58','2011-06-29 10:25:23','2011/06/29/03_23_58_212_file',0,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,6,'joy and happiness ;-)','3qQdwT7KI4',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,'ce24192e-a93a-43dd-9588-5fd85cb51957','bf566ce3-2cdd-4bf1-8950-a7bfbc49d3ab','http://www.linkedin.com/in/eddyboeve',0,0),(492,'writeme@philipfokker.com','','vocalharp7','Philip','Fokker',0,'','Editor/ columnist on new media, art, photography and video games at various magazines','2011-06-29 10:33:42','2011-06-29 10:42:58','2011/06/29/03_42_58_796_si006.jpg',0,1,NULL,NULL,81906560,6,'more than i take','hHMMuD7SmF','philipvince',NULL,'81906560-azsSMVgUroNtE8FmJCpR9A9yA7DUmLv3Q6e4K2Tl9','P2eSmuoRLpT7B1uiEgHwyv7ZRHWPmljVCJcY4jzdw',0,'d28d4369-40a9-4be7-ae78-86930a1e0371','1f49db6f-f42